{"message":"","data":[{"type":"1","id":"1346646883223658496","factor":"10","feedExts":[{"contentId":"1346646883223658496","content":{"content":"<p><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn3.dnaerapp.com\/2021\/1\/6\/10\/6562503941042a61e1b6499f7b7f676a160990057086626746.jpg\"><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn3.dnaerapp.com\/2021\/1\/6\/10\/6a5fa69bb3782b4bf5a17497c578d795160990059536368572.jpg\"><\/p>","secends":4026,"allowShare":true,"source":[],"title":"北京大学1996年数学分析试题及解答","systemStatus":true,"tags":["[]"],"userId":"1323881692674097152","scopeType":1,"visibleUserId":[],"cover":"","publishSecends":4026,"type":5,"articleShowType":2,"systemCreateTime":"2021-01-06 10:36:51","browses":226,"favours":10,"contentHotwordBeanList":[{"contentHotwordId":"1323925508456591360","word":"高数"}],"contentId":"1346646883223658496","comments":0,"checkStatus":1,"imageShowType":2,"allowComment":true,"cityName":"","forwards":0,"address":"","allowDownload":true},"exts":"最新内容:推荐","hasCollect":false,"hasDislike":false,"hasLike":false,"coins":0,"integral":26,"likes":[{"avatar":"https:\/\/cdn1.dnaerapp.com\/2021\/01\/04\/13\/9cf4797fdd6d4d62af89b88be7f0cf9a-0.jpg","userId":"1345915839130148864"},{"avatar":"https:\/\/cdn3.dnaerapp.com\/2020\/12\/21\/10\/24ccd0f1c9df443b344cd645a39af3d2160851895485769209.jpg","userId":"1340845283970392064"},{"avatar":"https:\/\/cdn3.dnaerapp.com\/2020\/10\/20\/14\/631c9ad213c119a2dd09a0fbf893cafa160317621574771840.jpg","userId":"1318442528950530048"},{"avatar":"https:\/\/cdn1.dnaerapp.com\/2020\/12\/30\/11\/74187deeaced4808851e1707a88e9bff-0.jpg","userId":"1344101079384104960"}],"user":{"status":2,"userLabels":[],"sex":1,"exts":"来自系统推荐！","userType":2,"hobbies":[],"avatar":"https:\/\/cdn3.dnaerapp.com\/2020\/11\/4\/17\/75efc3bfba20db3a36be9f5e6de8c545160448297074159580.jpg","userId":"1323881692674097152","dId":"237833","finalShowName":"速来学习","nickName":"速来学习","relation":{"hasSelf":false,"hasMyFan":false,"hasMyFocus":false,"hasRelation":false,"hasFriend":false,"reqUserId":"1323881692674097